Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheeze... Wheeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting worsen this fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has already reached their limit here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you old guy! You will be shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That person has been living for somebody for her whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make us people on the island happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,she sacrificed herself and was always standing by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know the weight of her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not somebody that you can take her life that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing there, you scrawny idiot shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S... Scrawny idiot shit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna die in vain right, you old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1254,1000)}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even able to use thymia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People with emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are always full of hatred and anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You are really ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugly is not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys who hide your faces and kill others have no right to say that to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will revenge Taisha-sama for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if my daughter was still alive, how she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,1000)}παγώνι
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pagóni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1144,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,1000)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Daímonas of Fallaina...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After all it's a superstition... So boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The livings inferior to the dusts in the sea of sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you ought to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of cuz, we know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were closed in a narrow island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and we know nothing about the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can influence nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get you out of that mud ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So! Fuck off you dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can never stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the internal moles!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Oni and I are together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we are the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mock us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK, Oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste my time with those mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have... always... been...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you to the world outside!
Comment: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How can thymia be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1382,1000)\i1}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,1000)}αὔρα
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How can aura appears at the {\i1}room of Nous{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni! Nibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,1000)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daímonas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How can it be happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...! It's because we broke a taboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,1000)}όρκα
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Orca's idea made it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,1000)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He waked up the Daímonas...! Caused by his...
Comment: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shaggy! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos! Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni! Oni! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asking you don't leave me alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but... it turned out to be I left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Buki... Aijiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,feel embarrassed with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I see you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you thought... if we can't help you get out of the mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we are nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But indeed... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than you may thought... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was satisfied with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm longing for the world outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just love to see the changeless sky and sea everyday, with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me who was nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't meet you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't be together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dust the world down, and show us the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.94,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,1000)}ολιβίνης
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Olivines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oli...vines?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.50,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The recorder of Fallaina, let's make a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please devote all the emotions of the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.41,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1432,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.41,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1146,1000)}άνθρωπος
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,on your island to the great Anthropos the Nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can promise that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.62,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1254,1000)}άνθρωπος
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.62,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,1000)}κόκαλο
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you the bone of Anthropos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.54,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1272,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.54,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,1000)}αίμα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have Blood with Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.85,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056,1000)}κόκαλο
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.85,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336,1000)}αίμα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can have both Kókkalo and Emma,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.26,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(764,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then Fallaina can get to a new stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I'll have to bring Lykos and Oni back to the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, is it pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel pain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because our {\i1}brains{\i0} feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We are shaken and bruised by the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why we make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can tweak the pain and get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We just {\i1}falsify the records of hearts{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can share the fragments of happiness that the Nous ate from other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and make it as if our own memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the emotion just like your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are able to get immersed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in a world everyone can be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The children of the whale, whose lives were that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:28.68,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rewrite your sorry stories with the power of Nous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewrite... the painful records?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.74,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sinners of the whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to relieve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But how will our yearnings be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have lost Sami, Taisha-sama, Nibi and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They have been with us, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the proves of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can never forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the pains and bitter experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are the records of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... you give me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep that promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to watch the future of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.49,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed, the sinners of the whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to the new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}July 17, 93 S.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The sandstorm since the morning had finally begun to calm in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.87,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\pos(1412,1000)}σκύλος
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}When we were trying to escape from the Skulax,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}contrary to the collapsing ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}the sea was so calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}It was really painful to leave the died fellow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}However, we kept them in our minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}promised we will never forget them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}and then we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Though we were not used to fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}we took up the weapons and resisted our destiny with our own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}There was no other way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}except fighting if we wanted to protect our paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Many friends died, and returned to the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}For me, I wanted to write down all these happenings,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}in order to have proves of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}This is, the responsibility and the meaning of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}as a survival, and as a recorder.
